thread.title: Jody Stack Carrodus
thread.title_full: MacCredit reviewed by Jody Stack Carrodus

author: Jody Stack Carrodus
title: Jody Stack Carrodus
text: MacCredit were so easy to deal with when we applied for dental funding for my husband. He had not seen a dentist for many years and was at the point of me divorcing him...LOL...he can now get the much needed work done and for the first time in a very long time smile. I highly recommend MacCredit
